  "body": "  The 2020 Census US Census Bureau, \"QuickFacts: Kitsap County, Washington, www.census.gov\/quickfacts\/fact\/table\/kitsapcountywashington\/PST045223 reports that Kitsap County, Washington, has a population of 275,612 people and covers 395.1 square miles of land. Find the population density as a unit rate of people per square mile.        "
