  "title": "",
  "body": "  A recipe calls for 3 tablespoons of sugar. A home chef is quadrupling the recipe. How much sugar will they need in cups?    They will need tablespoons of sugar.  We make use of the conversions that there are two tablespoons in an ounce and eight ounces in a cup.   The home chef should use of a cup of sugar.   "
